metadata.title: President Zardari, AJK legislators discuss issues, development projects

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Jun 12 (APP): A delegation of the Members of the Azad Jammu and Kashmir Legislative Assembly called on President Asif Ali Zardari here on Thursday. In the meeting, they discussed the overall situation in the AJK, besides apprising the president of the problems faced by the territory, provision of the facilities and development needs. President Zardari stressed the importance of prioritizing AJK's development and the well-being of its residents.
